JOHN JENDRUSIAK v. L. J. APPEL SONS, INC. [No. 12,

October Term, 1929.]

Decided October 31st, 1929.

Tbe cause was argued before Bokd, C. J., Urher, Adkiks, Oeeutt, Digges, Parke, and Sloak, JJ.

Daniel O. Joseph, witb whom was Abram O. Joseph on tbe brief, for tbe appellant. W. JjeRoy Ortel, for tbe appellee. Bokd, C. J.,

delivered tbe opinion of tbe Court, affirming tbe decree.
